{"pageProps":{"article":{"title":"A Mom-umental Mother’s Day Brunch","category":"On the Menu","subcategory":"Recipes","publish_date":"2018-05-10T07:00:00.000Z","full_thumbnail":"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9978.jpg?resize=355%2C230&ssl=1","mobile_thumbnail":"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9978.jpg?resize=980%2C647&ssl=1","description":"Your personal guide to the ultimate Mother's Day brunch.","content":"<div class=\"single-post-content\">\n            <p>Mother’s Day is right around the corner, and what better way to cherish your mom than by treating her with a breakfast in bed? If you’re like me and bad with showing your feelings through words, show them through food. You don’t have to be as skilled as your mom to whip up something delicious. I put together three simple recipes that will make the ultimate Mother’s Day meal and really show your mom how much you love her!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_82959\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-82959\" data-attachment-id=\"82959\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2018-05-10/a-mom-umental-mothers-day-brunch/img_9976/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9976.jpg?fit=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"IMG_9976\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9976.jpg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9976.jpg?fit=888%2C666&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"size-large wp-image-82959\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-co