"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"IMG_9979\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?fit=888%2C666&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"size-large wp-image-82962\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979-1024x768.jpg?resize=888%2C666\" alt=\"\" width=\"888\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=1832%2C1374&amp;ssl=1 1832w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=1376%2C1032&amp;ssl=1 1376w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=1044%2C783&amp;ssl=1 1044w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=632%2C474&amp;ssl=1 632w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?resize=536%2C402&amp;ssl=1 536w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?w=2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9979.jpg?w=1776 1776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-82962\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Rachel Lee / Daily Nexus</em></p></div>\n<p><strong>Eggs in a Basket</strong></p>\n<p>Ingredients:</p>\n<p>1 slice of bread<br>\n1 tbs butter<br>\n1 egg<br>\nKosher salt<br>\nFreshly ground black pepper</p>\n<p>Instructions:</p>\n<p>Heat pan to medium/high.<br>\nCut heart into center of bread (or use a heart-shaped cookie cutter if you have one) and take out the center piece.<br>\nMelt butter in a large pan.<br>\nButter both sides of the bread. Add bread and toast until golden brown on one side. Flip onto the other side.<br>\nCrack the egg into the center of the heart. Add salt and pepper to taste.<br>\nSet heat to low/medium and gently cook the egg until the egg whites are set and egg yolk is cooked to liking.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_82960\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-82960\" data-attachment-id=\"82960\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2018-05-10/a-mom-umental-mothers-day-brunch/img_9977/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?fit=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"IMG_9977\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?fit=888%2C666&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"size-large wp-image-82960\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977-1024x768.jpg?resize=888%2C666\" alt=\"\" width=\"888\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=1832%2C1374&amp;ssl=1 1832w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=1376%2C1032&amp;ssl=1 1376w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=1044%2C783&amp;ssl=1 1044w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=632%2C474&amp;ssl=1 632w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?resize=536%2C402&amp;ssl=1 536w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?w=2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IMG_9977.jpg?w=1776 1776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-82960\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Rachel Lee / Daily Nexus</em></p></div>\n<p><strong>Yogurt Parfait</strong></p>\n<p>Ingredients</p>\n<p>Yogurt of your liking (I used blueberry yogurt for this recipe)<br>\n1 sliced kiwi (or fruit of your choice!)<br>\nGranola<br>\nCoconut flakes<br>\nSliced almonds<br>\nHoney</p>\n<p>Instructions:</p>\n<p>Layer yogurt into glass (thickness of each layer is up to you!).<br>\nLayer granola, coconut flakes and sliced almonds.<br>\nDrizzle honey.<br>\nLayer sliced bananas.<br>\nRepeat until filled to liking.<br>\nRefrigerate and serve chilled.</p>\n<p>Mother’s Day is a time to celebrate and cherish your mom more than you already have during the rest of the year. Pull out all the stops by making these recipes and make sure to prepare them with lots of love. Wishing all the moms out there a fun Mother’s Day filled with lots of good food.</p><div class=\"h5ab-print-button-container\"><div class=\"h5ab-print-button h5ab-print-button-left\" style=\"cursor: pointer; color: #555\"><i class=\"fa fa-print fa-lg\"></i